<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.840364>
    dc:description "FIGURES 28 – 31. Dorsal view of habitus and aedeagi of Melanterius costipennis Lea and M. inconspicuus (Lea). 28 – 29: M. costipennis; 28: male (Tasmania, Hobart); 29: aedeagus (Victoria, Cobden). 30 – 31: M. inconspicuus; 30: male (New South Wales, Yengo NP); 31: adeagus (New South Wales, Yengo NP)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/840364/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

